headline: Mill City Announces Commencement of Options Trading on Cboe Exchange

(“Mill City” or the “Company”) (NASDAQ: MCVT) today announced that the Company’s common stock is available for options trading on the Cboe Global Markets (“Cboe”), effective August 22, 2025, under the ticker “MCVT”. headline: Longbridge Group Collaborates with Cboe to Expand Global Index Offering, Enhancing Investor Access to Key Market Data
summary: Longbridge Group, a leading financial technology innovator, today announced that it has added the Cboe Global Indices Feed to its data coverage, empowering its clients with advanced tools to navigate dynamic markets and strengthening Longbridge's position as a gateway to institutional grade insights for retail and professional investors alike.
